es/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afba354bcab5a42a47580e7d2d3951c8b2963391","tid":29337,"uid":49218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推🤛🏿"},{"pid":"25dffddd660a045747de4da6f68b9cf75a195b81","tid":29337,"uid":33969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"f184d6c325f068c7b8cfffd7ba707cb23dd6ccac","tid":29337,"uid":49218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕輕一推</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3af022077e39d8238404bfe5961d1fe18976e8","tid":29337,"uid":42465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3254723ab579f922846ce570e03babf7bdd2ec94","tid":29337,"uid":49218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8ad3c2d380e863791fbb816106c1a67a96473e","tid":29337,"uid":49218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:42:06.000Z","msg":"-第五章- 《蠢蠢欲動》<br />\n<br />\n「子良，再表演一次『那個』給我們看吧！」同班的蕭希道。<br />\n<br />\n「不能再做『那個』了，爸爸不喜歡我做。」子良拍着籃球說道。<br />\n<br />\n「但是有些人還沒看過呢！讓他們看一次吧！最後一次！」蕭希做着合掌並拜訪他，其他圍觀的同學也苦苦哀求，想看到傳說中的「那個」。<br />\n<br />\n他們口中說的「那個」指的是「灌籃」。雖然天狼吩咐過他不能太突出，但有時候子良都會趁著附近沒老師和太多人時做一些爸爸不批准他做的事情，上星期他「灌籃」時正好被好朋友蕭希看到。消息一會兒便傳到大半班也知道，為了不再讓消息傳開去，子良有時會私底下表演給他們看，並當成保密的條件。<br />\n<br />\n結果這次半推半就地答應了，再給他們表演了一次，子良在三分線外準備，子良眼神一變，野獸般的眼神出現，他立刻對着籃框跑起來，大約距離籃底兩米左右，他用右腳一躍而起，左手輕鬆把球灌進去，就像背上有翅膀飛起來一樣，即使一些同學不是第一次看，還是嘆為觀止。<br />\n<br />\n落地後他的眼神變回溫和了，道：「別再告訴他人了，我不會再做這個！」語氣中的堅決讓其他同學知道他心意已決，這真的是最後一次了。<br />\n<br />\n整個過程被同一班中的一群不良少年看見了，他們用邪惡和不肖的眼光看着剛才出盡風頭的王子良並交頭接耳地不知道在討論些甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n-第五章完-"},{"pid":"a20eba31122b82f3632407a01a23c7be25bb567c","tid":29337,"uid":49218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"pushpush<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79bc8addb004b957dbe42c67464b93472d0e450","tid":29337,"uid":35990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:50:06.000Z","msg":"唔錯，留名"},{"pid":"d49925379cdf80ba5c61456bcca08fefee6d1589","tid":29337,"uid":49218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:50:13.000Z","msg":"冇力一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6ffa862361999f63af27f24c675249bf163bc8","tid":29337,"uid":49218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔錯，留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}